ProSelect™ Selection Software







ProSelect™ Software Quick Start Guide


 




Heatcraft ProSelect™ Software

Close More Sales with Heatcraft ProSelect™ Software
Our new exclusive product selection software is designed to streamline the Heatcraft Refrigeration sales and estimating process for any commercial application. 
Created for wholesalers, contractors, engineers and distributors, ProSelect software provides fast access to accurate and up-to-date data. For most applications, no additional support documentation is required. The tool also allows users to calculate the energy savings potential of most products, so that facility managers can see the return on investment. It even gives users the flexibility to spec an entire job as a single quotation proposal.
Two versions are available
The full-featured version is available exclusively for download to registered Heatcraft Refrigeration customers on Access2Answers or upon request to 
proselect@heatcraftrpd.com with sales rep referral. This version allows users to create a real-time printed document with equipment pricing information, options and shipped-loose accessories, along with a full submittal specification of the products requested. 


The online version is accessible to the public using the link below.  It has limited features and does not create printed documents..


start using ProSelect software
Notice: We recommend running ProSelect software using Internet Explorer (9 or higher). Using other browsers may prevent software program from running.




